Test-case name: totem/tot-001
This test will check that Totem can playback youtube video
<ol>
<li title="action"> Open the dash and launch movie player by pressing the super key, and then entering ‘totem’</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">movie player should launch</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Press the F9 button</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">the sidebar should open</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Select 'Youtube' from the dropdown list enter 'ubuntu' as the search term and press find</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">videos should populate below in the search results</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Double-click the first video</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Video should begin playing in the window</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Press the pause button</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Video should pause and the button becomes a play button</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Press the play button</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Video should begin playing</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Press the play button</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Video should begin playing</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Press the full screen button</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Video should go to fullscreen and continue playing</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Press the full screen button</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Video should go to fullscreen and continue playing</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Hover your mouse along the button of the screen</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">The controls menu should display</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Move your mouse to the middle of the screen</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">The controls menu should disappear</li>
</ol>
<li title="action"> Press Escape</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">The video should return to normal size</li>
</ol>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Did the video respond properly to the commands given?</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<strong>
If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> 'failed' and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result</strong>